去你到住 你預左架啦 人地又唔係特別污穢 係就唔到你啲潔癖習慣姐<br />\n著住依啲朋友真係慘到仆街</blockquote><br />\n我無扮大方啊<br />\n事前已經有同佢講我有潔癖同好撚柒麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係你自己"},{"pid":"942c7bab46c8e6970a7c97c1c4aeeddf2e1f902c","tid":99704,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T22:36:23.000Z","msg":"今次撐樓主"},{"pid":"be776e4ef273815cbdfe83666e84b93391b3bfca","tid":99704,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T22:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次撐樓主</blockquote><br />\n多謝你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cb7d078adc95ec78311f34bb2f1cd08a550981","tid":99704,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T23:02:27.000Z","msg":"有無諗過係潔癖既問題<br />\n唔撚係人地有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c73f6c8358bad5ec9742ca17f9e0bbddf51882","tid":99704,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T23:04:04.000Z","msg":"潔癖撚真係麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又要招呼 又唔係好fd<br />\n屌又唔係 唔屌又唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有潔癖就唔好放人上黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要知道好多人係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e26ed5ee4b94fcd332cdaba5064f5a7f636f05","tid":99704,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T23:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔沖涼就上床真係接受唔到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明唔明當時親眼見到佢出完街就訓喺我張牀係有幾震撼同沮喪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f1f023e53985eff9b3cf90ccc37a2956a59771","tid":99704,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T23:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無諗過係潔癖既問題<br />\n唔撚係人地有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係有潔癖係麻鳩煩<br />\n但係上到去我地頭<br />\n跟返我少少規則同習慣都唔係好過份姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋去到人地到亂咁放人d野真係會搞到我搵唔返野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135ca3493131f1e2fb03a4413e2ecde52dbc4f8e","tid":99704,"uid":39426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T23:30:08.000Z","msg":"有潔癖個廚房會有幾污糟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你又講到自己成撚日抹, <br />\n外國撚又好少明火煮野好少油煙, <br />\n真係好唔match, <br />\n<br />\n去廁所又唔見你著第3對拖鞋? 廁所板有冇用即棄紙套?<br />\n<br />\n潔並唔係咁癖的"},{"pid":"2b75749f7700d5025e1a35157c1d8d36ea341920","tid":99704,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T23:33:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有潔癖個廚房會有幾污糟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你又講到自己成撚日抹, <br />\n外國撚又好少明火煮野好少油煙, <br />\n真係好唔match, <br />\n<br />\n去廁所又唔見你著第3對拖鞋? 廁所板有冇用即棄紙套?<br />\n<br />\n潔並唔係咁癖的</blockquote><br />\n我同幾個人夾租一間屋<br />\n共用廚房 <br />\n我住套房 所以廁所喺房入面 房同廁所用同一對拖鞋<br />\n廁所板我耐唔耐就會抹下<br />\nHousemate都係亞洲人 煮野好多油煙<br />\nMatch唔撚match自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1401e56b132bcb3bbed141c1c9ee3a4ad35c0c95","tid":99704,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T23:39:57.000Z","msg":"咁你唔鬧佢點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬧到佢知你唔鍾意咩好過谷鳩住啦"},{"pid":"7c3c21ea188a8086b7e5b69dac703cfafe6bead0","tid":99704,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T23:54:51.000Z","msg":"你潔癖撚同你個friend非潔癖撚，兩個人既習慣以至到價值觀根本就唔一樣<br />\n有時你好撚mind既野，你個friend自己唔mind所以冇留意到，都唔可以怪哂佢<br />\n<br />\ne.g.<br />\n你習慣：一定要個人乾乾淨淨先可以走上張床<br />\n佢習慣：平時番屋企見攰就攤上張床到<br />\n咁既話你個friend基本上唔會將「沖涼先」同「走上床」connect埋一齊，你唔講定先可能真係一下子唔會諗到咁多，咪同平時一樣想攤咪攤床<br />\n<br />\n如果你事先同佢溝通好哂一定會好好多，有時唔好以為人地下下知道你諗緊乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [img][/img]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：同你個friend身同感受&amp;(我諗己經)俾個潔癖撚friend訓練成為一個潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027d292034138ab23934c8c5f4516f7573084716","tid":99704,"uid":73805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:02:56.000Z","msg":"我好憎著拖鞋，有一次上潔癖fd度訓，入門口著完拖鞋坐低就忘記咗，成晚不停重複醒起要著拖鞋---搵返佢黎著---坐低起身唔記得咗著返，我覺得佢想殺咗我。<br />\n對冇呢個習慣既人黎講一對都好困難，樓主體諒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5691e03c7f6801a9ac7230038ac38c6b1185b9","tid":99704,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你唔鬧佢點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬧到佢知你唔鍾意咩好過谷鳩住啦</blockquote><br />\n我有講過有提過佢<br />\n但係下下都係咁講 <br />\n講到自己都覺得自己煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8b5e4e6183c83fe1192325afb3929b8c492405","tid":99704,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你潔癖撚同你個friend非潔癖撚，兩個人既習慣以至到價值觀根本就唔一樣<br />\n有時你好撚mind既野，你個friend自己唔mind所以冇留意到，都唔可以怪哂佢<br />\n<br />\ne.g.<br />\n你習慣：一定要個人乾乾淨淨先可以走上張床<br />\n佢習慣：平時番屋企見攰就攤上張床到<br />\n咁既話你個friend基本上唔會將「沖涼先」同「走上床」connect埋一齊，你唔講定先可能真係一下子唔會諗到咁多，咪同平時一樣想攤咪攤床<br />\n<br />\n如果你事先同佢溝通好哂一定會好好多，有時唔好以為人地下下知道你諗緊乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [img][/img]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：同你個friend身同感受&amp;amp;(我諗己經)俾個潔癖撚friend訓練成為一個潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拖鞋嗰方面未嚟之前已經講咗佢知<br />\n但可能佢唔習慣我嘅生活方式啦<br />\n牀嗰方面好後悔無講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddf603dfadef9d7a197cee915f0a4dd77ce934a","tid":99704,"uid":39426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有潔癖個廚房會有幾污糟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你又講到自己成撚日抹, <br />\n外國撚又好少明火煮野好少油煙, <br />\n真係好唔match, <br />\n<br />\n去廁所又唔見你著第3對拖鞋? 廁所板有冇用即棄紙套?<br />\n<br />\n潔並唔係咁癖的</blockquote><br />\n我同幾個人夾租一間屋<br />\n共用廚房 <br />\n我住套房 所以廁所喺房入面 房同廁所用同一對拖鞋<br />\n廁所板我耐唔耐就會抹下<br />\nHousemate都係亞洲人 煮野好多油煙<br />\nMatch唔撚match自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁講我就明"},{"pid":"182c7b7d1e50c90511322b3d7a901a260b84a564","tid":99704,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:23:18.000Z","msg":"我呢，叫得朋友上黎住就唔理佢點玩架喇，不過入屋除鞋就一定要，其他就由理，因為我都預左"},{"pid":"d82e4dc971cee2323f97bdded58f86a12c3bfc56","tid":99704,"uid":343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:28:23.000Z","msg":"拖鞋個下麻煩啲 淨係分出街同屋企著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔沖涼訓落床 人地張床我都會咁做 自己就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9340f4c2d9d84f078b5c70b53a44546d1bbbc82f","tid":99704,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好憎著拖鞋，有一次上潔癖fd度訓，入門口著完拖鞋坐低就忘記咗，成晚不停重複醒起要著拖鞋---搵返佢黎著---坐低起身唔記得咗著返，我覺得佢想殺咗我。<br />\n對冇呢個習慣既人黎講一對都好困難，樓主體諒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都明一時間係好難叫佢跟我生活方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係依幾日谷住谷住好辛苦忍唔住呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f700de7d88cec6897ad0690a85f3bb03b2eed6","tid":99704,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:35:40.000Z","msg":"幫樓主唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有潔癖就唔好俾人上黎住啦<br />\n對方根本就係正常人 係你麻煩咋<br />\n<br />\n不過事到如今 <br />\n除非你想少個friend<br />\n唔係就忍下啦"},{"pid":"feab8fc1456573235f6c3b9fe26c2070f4a8d5bc","tid":99704,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拖鞋個下麻煩啲 淨係分出街同屋企著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔沖涼訓落床 人地張床我都會咁做 自己就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你訓人地張牀有無問過人先?<br />\n無嘅話你真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}